1. Download newest bootloader firmware version from 
   http://embedded-creations.com/projects/attiny85-usb-bootloader-overview/attiny85-usb-bootloader-downloads/
2. Extract content of the firmware folder
3. Apply patches
   patch bootloaderconfig.h < bootloaderconfig.h.diff
   # the patch below adds usbtiny programmer
   patch Makefile < Makefile.new 
4. make
